---
// Homepage-element dat verwijst naar /consultancy: donker paneel met propositie, instapmomenten en teamfoto.
---

<section class="py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2f6e 0%, #2554a0 55%, #2d5fa8 100%);">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[350px] h-[350px] bg-emerald-400/15 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/3 pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[300px] h-[300px] bg-accent-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/4 pointer-events-none"></div>

      <div class="relative px-8 sm:px-12 py-12 lg:py-16 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_1fr] lg:gap-14 lg:items-center">

        <!-- Copy -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-300 mb-3">Consultancy</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight leading-tight">
            ISO implementeer je zelf.<br />
            <span class="text-emerald-300">Of samen met ons.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-5 text-primary-100/85 leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
            Met de portal doorloop je het hele traject volledig zelfstandig. Consultancy is dan ook geen vereiste, maar een keuze. Wil je persoonlijke begeleiding, dan zijn er twee vormen: losse hulp op uurbasis of een volledig begeleid traject.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap gap-2.5">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-full">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-300"></span>
              Vanaf de start
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-full">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-300"></span>
              Halverwege je traject
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-full">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-300"></span>
              Tegen de audit aan
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-primary-100/60">Elk moment is een goed moment om in te stappen.</p>

          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-5">
            <a href="/consultancy" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-950 bg-white hover:bg-primary-50 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-lg">
              Ontdek de mogelijkheden
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/></svg>
            </a>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <img src="/falko.jpg" alt="Falko, ISO-consultant" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-white/40" style="object-position: center 15%;" loading="lazy" />
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-100/80 leading-snug">Persoonlijke begeleiding<br class="sm:hidden" /> door onze eigen consultants</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Foto -->
        <div class="relative mt-10 lg:mt-0">
          <img src="/images/consultancy-overleg.jpg" alt="Overleg met een Control One consultant" class="w-full h-64 sm:h-80 lg:h-[380px] object-cover rounded-2xl border border-white/15 shadow-2xl shadow-black/30" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="mt-4 sm:mt-0 sm:absolute sm:-bottom-4 sm:left-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-primary-900/20 px-5 py-3.5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 text-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-4.5 h-4.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </span>
            <p class="text-sm text-primary-900/80"><strong class="text-primary-950">Een vaste pakketprijs</strong> of op uurbasis, jij kiest</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
